<h3 id="调教-vga" class="heading"><a href="#调教-vga" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="章节： 调教 VGA" tabindex="-1"></a><span>调教 VGA</span></h3>
<p>时序好难调<span class="mojikumi-line-start">（</span></p>
<p>Quartus 报的时序错误不要无视<span class="mojikumi-line-end">。</span></p>
<p>时钟频率太高容易寄<span class="mojikumi-line-end">，</span>可以调低点<span class="mojikumi-line-end">。</span></p>
