<p>如果信号偏了两三个周期<span class="mojikumi-line-end">，</span>不用管它为什么会偏<span class="mojikumi-line-end">，</span>把它偏回来就行<span class="mojikumi-line-start">（</span></p>
<p>尽量不要用组合逻辑输出<span class="mojikumi-line-end">，</span>可以加个 buffer<span class="mojikumi-line-end">。</span></p>]]></content>
